          "formulaExpression": "a^3 + b^3 = (a+b)(a^2 - ab + b^2)",
          "calculation": "Numerator = $(a+b)(a^2 + b^2 - ab) = a^3 + b^3$",
          "result": "$a^3 + b^3$"
        },
        {
          "stepNumber": 2,
          "explanation": "Recognize the denominator as $(a^2 + ab + b^2)$, which also equals $\\frac{a^3 - b^3}{a - b}$.",
          "formula": null,
          "formulaExpression": "\\frac{(a+b)(a^2 + b^2 - ab)}{(a^2 + b^2 + ab)} = \\frac{a^3 + b^3}{a^2 + ab + b^2} = a - b",
          "calculation": "Using $a^3 - b^3 = (a-b)(a^2 + ab + b^2)$ ... but here numerator = $a^3 + b^3$",
